名次 城市 每月寬頻價格 供應商數量

79 [Syktyvkar](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syktyvkar
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syktyvkar") 66 2

80 [Nizhnevartovsk](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nizhnevartovsk
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nizhnevartovsk") 67 1

